name: Split Decisions
description: the "Split Decisions" are the shades that will instantly make you the most popular person in the room. A full strip of mirrors divides the vision into two panels which creates an overall visual orgy.

name: Common Cents
description: In a world where common sense aint so common, the COMMON CENTS shades are the appropriate replacement. Highlighted by the most discarded & forgotten form of American currency, the penny, these shades serve as a copper-colored orgy on your face.

name: Mistress
description: Its not about what you do, Its how you do it! Yes he has a wife and 2 kids.... But he spends his vacation with you and 2 Benz. The new age Mistress is well kept, knows her place, and is happy in knowing that at the end of the day she gets all of him minus the bills.

name: Return of the Ankh's
description:
I'm a recovering undercover over-lover
recovering from a love I can't get over
recovering undercover over-lover
and now my common law lover thinks he wants another

And I'd lie for you
I'd cry for you
and pop for you
and break for you
and hate for you
And I'll hate you too
If you want me too

I'd pray for you
crochet for you
Make it from scratch for you
Leave off the latch for you
Go to the store for you
Do it some more for you
The way you want me to
Yes I'm a fool for you...

name: Electrix Animal
description: Why did the zebra cross the road? So it could make love at a electric plant and birth these shades. The Electrix Animal is not for the purpose of freeing the animal in you, but rocking it casually upon your eyes.
